<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Sapna aw gi ngai un,
 &quot;Tuni'n kuo kuon ding?
 Ka nasepna hawla,
 Niel loa pang ding?
 Kuo a gal matawnga,
 Ka puonlap dawm ding?
 Pathien leh A thutak,
 Panpih a do ding?

[V2]
 Isu'n puonlap nuoi ah, sepaih ma A huoi;
 Galzo hiting, dikna'n khawvel luoh suok ding.

[V3]
 2. Pathien hatna muongin,
 Gal zawh macheng in;
 Setan lawi chu do-in,
 Kigalvan hitiu;
 Thienthona leh thutak,
 Panpih a do in;
 Pathien dinga do di'n,
 Pang khawm chiet I hiu.

[V4]
 3. Ngai un, a thawmgiu chuh,
 Lasa'n chieh zel ui;
 I Puipa, I Lalpau,
 Chu lopi henla;
 Gamla leh naia te,
 Lungtup kibang in;
 Galdo di'n a kuon ui,
 A aw giu ngai un!</lyrics>
<title>JESUS LEADS HIS ARMY</title>
<hymn_number>317</hymn_number>
</song>